                          <lb n="6"/>οὐ <unclear>μέγ</unclear>α· <unclear>κ</unclear>αὶ <placeName ref="#lato"><unclear>Λ</unclear>ατὼς</placeName> γὰρ ἐνέγκατο τόνδ<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied> <w lemma="σοφιστής">σοφιστὴ<unclear>ν</unclear></w>
