                          <lb n="9"/><unclear>Μν</unclear>ασ<unclear>τ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">οκ</supplied>λέους ὃν <supplied reason="lost">ἅ</supplied>πᾶς <rs type="institution" subtype="social_group" role="good_relations_or_behaviour" key="demos" ref="#lato"><w lemma="δῆμος">δῆμος</w></rs> ἐπῳκτίσατο·
                          <lb n="10"/>οὐ γ<unclear>ὰρ</unclear> <supplied reason="lost">ἐπλ</supplied>ήρωσεν γήραι βίον, ὡς δέ τις ἀστὴρ
